  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Aurion</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dragonlord Aurion by Jota Saraiva.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6a/Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/350px-Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6a/Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/525px-Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6a/Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg/700px-Dragonlord_Aurion_by_Jota_Saraiva.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Aurion, by Jota Saraiva</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragonlord\" title=\"Dragonlord\">Dragonlord</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Emperor_of_Valyria\" title=\"Emperor of Valyria\">Emperor of Valyria</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valyrians\" title=\"Valyrians\">Valyrian</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_102_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">102&#160;BC</a> or shortly after<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_peninsula\" title=\"Valyrian peninsula\">Valyrian peninsula</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Aurion</b> was one of the few <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonlords\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragonlords\">dragonlords</a> who survived the <a href=\"/index.php/Doom_of_Valyria\" title=\"Doom of Valyria\">Doom of Valyria</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aurion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to histories of <a href=\"/index.php/Qohor\" title=\"Qohor\">Qohor</a>, he raised forces from Qohorik colonists and declared himself first <a href=\"/index.php/Emperor_of_Valyria\" title=\"Emperor of Valyria\">Emperor of Valyria</a>. Atop his <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, he flew south to lay claim to what remained of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyria</a> and reestablish the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Freehold</a> along with his thirty thousand men. Neither Emperor Aurion nor his host were ever seen again.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aurion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_doom_of_valyria.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: The Doom of Valyria.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404074710\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.255 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 467/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10449/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5259/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 983/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 677/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.75 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  245.516      1 -total\n 97.35%  239.006      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.70%  237.415      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.83%   26.584     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.67%    9.019      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.00%    4.920      1 Template:Ref\n  1.36%    3.342      1 Template:Date\n  1.29%    3.167      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.59%    1.454      3 Template:Main_other\n  0.58%    1.426      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18589-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404074710 and revision id 295258\n -->\n",
